pageProduct.name: SUP ReSUP Dial Weekly Organiser
pageProduct.description:
General Information

SUP RESUP Dial Weekly Organiser - Pop your weekly vitamins in this RESUP organiser.

RESUP Your Vitamins

Hey what SUP?
Cool vitamin organisers do exist! Pop your week's worth of SUPs into this RESUP dial and you might actually remember to take your vitamins. Each day holds 3-4 SUPs so your health game will be on point whether it's Monday to Friyay.

Week of SUPs Supported - 7.
Holds 3-4 SUPs per day.
Available in 3 colours.

RESUP

Boxed Contents: 3 Colours of SUP

Size: 1 Pack

KEY FEATURES

• Holds 3-4 SUPs per day
• Available in 3 colours
• Organise your vitamins!

Directions

How to fill:
1. Open side flap
2. Carefully lift and pull the lid forward, exposing open compartments
3. Fill up with your weekly SUPs
4. Place lid back on and click into position
5. Close side flap and you're all set!

How to use:
1. Hold RESUP flat and press the middle white button to rotate the days
2. Flip open side flap and POP out your SUPs
3. #THATSWHATSUP
